parts.text: This is an invoice from Sliced Invoices (DEMO) to Test Business for web design services.  The invoice number is INV-3337, the order number is 12345, and the invoice date is January 25, 2016, with a due date of January 31, 2016. The total amount due is $93.50.  The invoice details one service: Web Design (1 hour at $85.00), with a tax of $8.50 added.  The bank details for payment (ANZ Bank, ACC and BSB numbers) are provided at the bottom.  Late payment fees of 5% per month apply.
